verbose_text: The glycosylation profiles of the SOSIP.664 H72C-H564C, SOSIP.664 A73C-A561C, and both SOSIP.v5 trimers were all similar to those of SOSIP.664 and SOSIP.v4.1, with oligomannose glycoforms dominating (61%-64%) and, in particular, Man 8 GlcNAc 2 and Man 9 GlcNAc 2 glycans (XREF_TABLE; XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY F).
